snippet.title: Pokémon Crystal - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo 3DS
snippet.description:
Originally released for the Game Boy™ Color system in 2000, Pokémon Crystal makes its return on the Virtual Console on January 26th, 2018. Explore the Johto region again—or for the first time! Available only on the Nintendo 3DS family of systems.

Learn more about Pokémon Crystal for Nintendo 3DS! https://goo.gl/Viwkic
